  => "  t3:   single 141 vs ensemble 75 (47% lower)"
  => "interpretation: seed=6 was OUTLIER in some topologies"
  => "implication: iter-36 r=0.99 finding NEEDS ensemble re-validation"
  => "single-seed bias revealed across iter-31/32/36"

